的敌意后与厄立特里亚达成和平协议后获得了诺贝尔奖，但他没有采取任何措施缓解紧张局势，而是主要诉诸武力平息异议。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;他因要求&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/174dGxWUgv1O6wzBF6ITInkyXW44oO_LGaOYU95mCZ6oD5AdMz1xj0KE9rIY3uk4HZMKFlkRv_E2fMs-muKnJi5xE75S5T6xWll4rfptryMiAcBgFhX-Ys7sqzeZJCfS27IcdMtHcLW-rB69_rBzjD-_5ZhJhw4rcqAfKflqeMdxhyk2WsbxmXnUFp9P7VeuiliJaHAhI1pONy_eEl3YtVmmQxGDcvvarXcXQ3jJUHS0htqFbppsiqlHoRRMon_r9PXlcTqufDHV883G0jfPpy-Gw8552Tz0Y5-qt4hCP6HiabR4Km212rjtRsniIxT1rn2kBU9r66DatXfcIQ5auHdYkbyQMZO9doUzxqa6exveYl0IoKWSAyvXesGnokPIbQnWIUucJgb_vdpqYyQs2F7so3mYrEj4-quhxMC8Dh0m5U5abfVpA1o2elTxNxLXlBzlwH5ZGtCacJd0U8gdW7q1o7YsiDs3IspHGnE09NdS-j1N4nw1_30hfShY4Wde39OlImSUyHaJxfPCk_hCOrWxXzM-VQ/JVexBt4rOz2BXGaziJnk0ejVWXQnw-_B/21" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="为什么埃塞俄比亚争夺红海通道会激怒索马里"&gt;直接出海而&lt;/a&gt;激怒了索马里和厄立特里亚，因在尼罗河支流上&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/Ze9LHx50ftEoey4KkYI_KwR083HpIV9QAAkbH1pt7EkJzwR6hByeK3NZPd6g54TNiU6kRdaRZpfKlbP7dXRWKLAaV8rfb5KaH9aaiL8pdhCQRJYHSox6HO6qUCqN8RTEfc43wMAMbBN-TOHfggBwjHeC_z9JTm3AndKfq_qhMv-H-lChh91NZrgYgHTHH2bs0cHcdaME1312GmIcB7QXGbRS3QKSphV4LXaSg_eMVAwUKh-qxY-GB0wcBOl1pqAxJ9AF9UwXcAozJLcoiJhzGJujwRXXYA9WB52w10Yf1ygYMj4aWRAR6Jzf5Sznwzcd8DbmaOI4FVMTiLcnyEnurL-fHSMaDe1LzNyFcmfzHquZPiV3jNGS3PP99zW9T-4DhPso4EtjHQh6H0_-a0ATyPY5EnszxzbEG7g_4sYLM-PTnoeNN_nX9WGsJoRjVGhNtEzuYtuSnYcp5qmfqO3n9nOPIRI9VYtbMy1zRBZ4M5GpOGn2gIty2litdlxp7gAq3brDZqqoDGV45wiCpiflxYDOJSaQ51GMHLF-kghF2dk/Xb-uA3r_GTB87Tn4PZde1-Ji5-cJF4c-/21" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="为什么埃塞俄比亚耗资 50 亿美元的尼罗河大坝激怒了邻国"&gt;修建一座巨大水坝&lt;/a&gt;而激怒了埃及，并招致苏丹军方指责其在该国内战中支持民兵。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;地区外交官今年早些时候警告称，埃塞俄比亚和厄立特里亚之间的关系急剧恶化，增加了&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/Mad9M7Cc1Pr0qWhbME7U2of38UZV-mE-IEwCEJQkJLV0Ozd0HkO2tGJmPpzIiuWiRZQDQeF__k5bHZpWKK603yNBxXhhzQrE8rmthuaF1Rgl1YwdDVpPgCDpy971gw